textAnnotations.description:
Practically a shore job. Cheer up." She wiped
her
eyes
and reached for her address book, "gill
write do those agents and try to get a flat in
Alverstoke," she said. "But I don't know what
fill will say about leaving her school. It's a
blessing that facky's off to boarding school.
And all the trouble you're taken with the
garden!
